{
  "stem": "27509.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And therefore, even in terms of, of the cultural basis for existence, they were cut off like, like, like Vienna was after the-- after the First World War when the-- when the-- when the, the Hapsburg Empire fell, fell to pieces and the Hinterland was completely taken away from them.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were just a big city like a white elephant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was the Wilno situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But, but in terms of, of, you know, the Jewish situation was only-- it affected the, the, the upper classes, in terms of the value system of the government, of the Russian government.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But it did not affect the people as Jews, as Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I have managed to, to communicate with my-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with my uncle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was an extraordinary thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The neighbor-- a young man, a neighbor in our house-- also ran away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was an only son.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He ran way to Wilno.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I met him in Wilno.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he told me the story, the extraordinary story, what happened to my family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because my father finally decided to leave Poland, but again, with the same illogicality in which he behaved first.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't say that with disrespect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He made a decision and left his mother and his family behind and crossed the border on his own.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was caught on the border, which wasn't extraordinary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was jailed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when he was interrogated, he had to tell them who he was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And by the nature of the fact that he had such a great enterprise, having a few knitting machines in his best room in the house, he was a capitalist.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was jailed for three years for crossing the border and for his capitalist past.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
